Node->state, parent, action
state (where we are)-current actor, parent(where we are coming from)-previous actor, action(from which way we arrived here)-films

path.reverse() #putting things in order
we should use this line to avoid outputs like this:
Name: morgan freeman
Name: emma watson
2 degrees of separation.
1: Morgan Freeman and Emma Watson starred in The Tale of Despereaux
2: Emma Watson and Dustin Hoffman starred in Outbreak

